headline: Smurfit Westrock (NYSE:SW) Sees 11% Dip As Board Member Dmitri Stockton Departs
summary: Recent developments at Smurfit Westrock (NYSE:SW) include Dmitri Stockton's impending departure from the board and an emphasis on mergers and acquisitions following the company's fourth quarter results announcement. Over the past week, Smurfit Westrock experienced a 10.64% decline in share price, which occurred despite a significant increase in both sales and net income. Concurrently, key indices like the S&P 500 and Nasdaq have reported ongoing weekly declines, with broader market trends...
